caption.center: PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN, PLAINTIFF-Appellee, v. MURAD WILLIAMS,

opinion.posture: Appeal from the Court of Appeals No. 268119.
opinion.opinion_text:
Leave to Appeal Denied December 13, 2006.
The defendant has failed to meet the burden of establishing entitlement to relief under MCR 6.508(D).
KELLY, J. I would remand this case for resentencing.
